{"tid":588314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無ching投左建制等食花生","createTime":"2018-03-11T06:35:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T07:19:33.000Z","uid":20241,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9eb415b035a8c34b71d3a0801000f4b718ba94e9","tid":588314,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T06:35:27.000Z","msg":"有台妹老婆<br />\n香港有個供斷單位<br />\n打算搵多幾年錢就過台灣<br />\n雖然個心支持港獨台獨<br />\n不過老實講香港變成點我完全無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次特登投建制 希望快啲赤化<br />\n一黎有得食花生<br />\n二黎到時啲港豬走難去台灣我就印印腳係個邊做老屎忽<br />\n又可以搵佢地錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n急不及待好想玩玩了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278a8166302da730280fb7f3f6e4292db656a6dd","tid":588314,"uid":89134,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T06:41:04.000Z","msg":"投咗玉蛾"},{"pid":"2a8264ff6e1d043c4d7fc627da6bb0203256d22d","tid":588314,"uid":91214,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T06:49:14.000Z","msg":"等睇台灣收埋皮 應該仲好玩"},{"pid":"b47e7421bf9a5a0ee672af66113c4b6bb0b22e71","tid":588314,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a8264ff6e1d043c4d7fc627da6bb0203256d22d","tid":588314,"uid":91214,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T06:49:14.000Z","msg":"等睇台灣收埋皮 應該仲好玩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T06:49:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b52f46219a64f152c1caa9612874ebb39c6fe335","tid":588314,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a8264ff6e1d043c4d7fc627da6bb0203256d22d","tid":588314,"uid":91214,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T06:49:14.000Z","msg":"等睇台灣收埋皮 應該仲好玩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T07:01:00.000Z","msg":"你收大台灣都未收啦on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f21e9c7324407ec87d45d8dabfa0bba354558bd","tid":5